---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Kyrux">
  <section class="panel mx-auto max-w-3xl p-6 md:p-8">
    <p class="chip mb-4">About Me</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-100">Kyrux</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
      I focus on practical web exploitation and offensive security. Currently grinding CTFs to sharpen 
      my pentesting skills. My goal is simple: turn complex exploit chains into clear, reproducible workflows for everyone.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
      I use this site as a digital lab notebook to archive my CTF workflows, deep dives, and concise 
      field notes. Practical, reproducible, and built for the offensive mindset.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/70 p-4">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">Focus Areas</h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
          <li>Web Exploitation</li>
          <li>CTF Player</li>
          <li>Pentesting</li>
          <li>Offensive Tooling</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/70 p-4">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">Contact</h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
          <li>
            GitHub:
            <a href="https://github.com/kyrux29" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"> @kyrux29</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            Status:
            <span class="text-cyan-300"> Open for security collaborations</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
